-- Ben-Israel Prefers 'Word of Mouth' Over Advertising (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2012-04-03T13:20:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-03/ben-israel-prefers-word-of-mouth-over-advertising-audio-.html
Ron Ben-Israel, the owner of Ron 
Ben-Israel Cakes, and the host of "Sweet Genius" on the Food 
Network, says he prefers "word of mouth" referrals to his 
business rather than advertising.  Ben-Israel also discusses the
operation of his small business of making custom wedding cakes. 
 Ben-Israel talked to Vonnie Quinn and Roben Farzad on Bloomberg
Radio's "The Hays Advantage" on April 2, 2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 16:40
 